       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CHARY2K.
       AUTHOR. SID WAITE.
       DATE-COMPILED. TODAY.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT FILEIN ASSIGN TO "S30". 
           SELECT FILEOUT ASSIGN TO "S35" ORGANIZATION
           LINE SEQUENTIAL.
       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD  FILEIN. 
       01  FILEIN01 PIC X.
       FD  FILEOUT. 
       01  FILEOUT01 PIC X(80).
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 CNTR PIC 99.
       01 TAB8001.
          02 TAB80 PIC X OCCURS 80 TIMES.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       P0.
           OPEN INPUT FILEIN OUTPUT FILEOUT.
           PERFORM A1.
       P1. MOVE SPACE TO FILEIN01
           READ FILEIN AT END GO TO P2.
           IF CNTR = 80
           MOVE TAB8001 TO FILEOUT01
           WRITE FILEOUT01
           PERFORM A1.
           ADD 1 TO CNTR
           MOVE FILEIN01 TO TAB80(CNTR)
           GO TO P1.
        A1.
           MOVE 0 TO CNTR
           MOVE SPACE TO TAB8001.
        P2.
           MOVE TAB8001 TO FILEOUT01
           WRITE FILEOUT01
           CLOSE FILEOUT STOP RUN.
